{"tid":1747881,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"觀塘巴絲打麻煩入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-11-23T11:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T00:29:30.000Z","uid":169040,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8257ff6b94beebcd9edaeffe63688ea6747fe4c9","tid":1747881,"uid":169040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:57:39.000Z","msg":"自細住係觀塘<br />\n每次選舉都無失望<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為根本無期望過</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n年年區議會選舉，來來去都係老屎忽或者老屎忽第二代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n年年立法會選舉，都係三個建制二個泛民<br />\n班建制根本坐定定嬴梗<br />\n觀塘好似比大陸仲大陸<br />\n<br />\n睇睇數據<br />\n2015年 區議會選舉 建制 vs 非建制 vs 獨立(政治取向不明) : 66,253 vs 46,249 vs 2,750<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8uQbZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8uQbZc.jpg&h=91ab6c95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n真係好絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係<br />\n2016年 立法會選舉 建制 vs 泛民 vs熱狗: 91,050 vs 83,633 vs 18,929<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m917ecC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm917ecC.jpg&h=959a3fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實觀塘又唔係真係咁藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點解區議會藍都發黑？<br />\n係因為有<strong>１１個選區自動當選</strong>，<strong>即係１１個區既選民無得表態</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果呢１１個選區有得表達的話，咁結果會係點？<br />\n假設立法會既投票取向跟區議會差唔多的話<br />\n咁結果會點呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxbK0SV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxbK0SV.jpg&h=8e28582c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n換言之會有多幾個非建制入局<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我得承認觀塘都真係幾藍<br />\n係2015年區議會有多好區建制都大勝<br />\n相反，泛民/非建制都嬴得好辛苦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kGqLLjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGqLLjG.jpg&h=5b8bf6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過今年有變數<br />\n1)觀塘市中心重建<br />\n2)安達安泰都入哂伙<br />\n究竟孰好孰壞我真係唔知<br />\n<br />\n但我真係唔想觀塘再被建制操控<br />\n- 觀塘重建攪得一鍋泡<br />\n- 協和街月華街高價天橋無人出聲<br />\n- 無聊音樂噴水池<br />\n<br />\n最後，都要講一個殘酷既事實俾大家聽<br />\n雖然話好多年青人登記咗做選民，數目冠絕其他組別<br />\n但實情是如果比較2019年同2015年選民年齡結構既變化原來係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CmOUDGK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmOUDGK.jpg&h=33f2929a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L1KTUe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL1KTUe4.jpg&h=25c58f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來最多增長係26-30歲別組<br />\n但大家唔好忽略長者部份<br />\n總之....都係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一票不能少</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:無接受過專業統計學訓練，以上分析純粹以選舉事務處網站數據，再以excel計算<br />\n此外，由於2015年同2019年區議會選區不完全相同，2015年區議會選舉同2016立法會選舉既票站也有所出入，所以估算未必準確"},{"pid":"e57999647d529231a5138bad7635d4a183a1913b","tid":1747881,"uid":227301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:05:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c88db47d67c6712a9e3ebb94d77511ecc83f38b","tid":1747881,"uid":323228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8257ff6b94beebcd9edaeffe63688ea6747fe4c9","tid":1747881,"uid":169040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci