rc=\"https://na.cx/i/kGqLLjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkGqLLjG.jpg&h=5b8bf6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過今年有變數<br />\n1)觀塘市中心重建<br />\n2)安達安泰都入哂伙<br />\n究竟孰好孰壞我真係唔知<br />\n<br />\n但我真係唔想觀塘再被建制操控<br />\n- 觀塘重建攪得一鍋泡<br />\n- 協和街月華街高價天橋無人出聲<br />\n- 無聊音樂噴水池<br />\n<br />\n最後，都要講一個殘酷既事實俾大家聽<br />\n雖然話好多年青人登記咗做選民，數目冠絕其他組別<br />\n但實情是如果比較2019年同2015年選民年齡結構既變化原來係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CmOUDGK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmOUDGK.jpg&h=33f2929a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L1KTUe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL1KTUe4.jpg&h=25c58f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來最多增長係26-30歲別組<br />\n但大家唔好忽略長者部份<br />\n總之....都係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一票不能少</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:無接受過專業統計學訓練，以上分析純粹以選舉事務處網站數據，再以excel計算<br />\n此外，由於2015年同2019年區議會選區不完全相同，2015年區議會選舉同2016立法會選舉既票站也有所出入，所以估算未必準確"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:05:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>麻煩連登以外幫手文宣，<br />\n以下正皮、加推、幫手做，時間無多<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出街全部對家街站，死得啦，麻煩認真幫推呢個整合左既行動PO啦，再唔做的野輸死喇：</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>【行動post】《緊急》全民選舉文宣+鍵盤戰</strong></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743618</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><ins>原PO<br />\n選舉文宣！文宣！文宣呀！唔夠對家多呀！的牆無曬喇！</ins></span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezmgyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezmgyS</a>"},{"pid":"fe9a28a26cfd68b54246352b7cce3d960cc4c3b1","tid":1747881,"uid":169040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"唔推唔緊要<br />\n最緊要投票"},{"pid":"e4f9c990bd51d34b5e0766a51d8dc1daeecc2103","tid":1747881,"uid":169040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T23:45:46.000Z","msg":"要光復觀塘呀"},{"pid":"0f2434129a71e2ac9e05ebadcf485a11793f5251","tid":1747881,"uid":169040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T00:29:30.000Z","msg":"而家睇返立法會取向<br />\n都幾反映出到該區區議會的取向<br />\n會win的真係 win<br />\n但如果建制小勝的<br />\n係高投票率下了係可以返盤"}]}